{"tid":1369643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[長期置頂 ]727 最終安全路線圖","createTime":"2019-07-26T17:59:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T07:55:18.000Z","uid":264724,"like":65,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"f6a7a55824573fb89e76364634b1d546bd79fc52","tid":1369643,"uid":264724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:59:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最終冇大台</span> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但今日我哋幾萬人亂行元朗<br />\n唔駛黑社會同鄉紳<br />\n我哋自己都會<strong>自亂陣腳</strong> <br />\n亂行一通 分分鐘行入地雷 而不知 咁就送頭</span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n所以 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">遊行路線只得一條</span> 行完可以再行 因為係一個loop <br />\n唔理你幾點去<span style=\"color: blue;\"> 最多人話3點 </span>跟住呢個looper 行 就一定冇死 <br />\n<br />\n1. 元朗西鐵站 <br />\n2. 大馬路 順手買餅 <br />\n3. 見到民政事務處轉右 <br />\n4. 入媽廟路 直行 或行 屏會街 出番大街 <br />\n5. 轉右 行媽橫路 入朗屏站走 或者 <br />\n6. 原直路 (安樂路) 入返 元朗地鐵站返屋企 <br />\n又或者再入返大馬路 行多次無限輪迴 到六點<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">快啲分享去 各大tg</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cf1qkGm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCf1qkGm.jpg&h=ae4ab00a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b108a83a3a46fc7de6c264305031b69a028176bb","tid":1369643,"uid":264724,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:01:14.000Z","msg":"諗咗成晚 都係覺得呢條路線最安全 <br />\n因為有兩個位走 <br />\n同埋行極都係大路"},{"pid":"bcd0114b8a9d57b7826ccf30a112b6ff46603596","tid":1369643,"uid":264724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:01:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"08b1b44610d0187ea9b051864bc9b2031105c7bc","tid":1369643,"uid":36120,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:01:49.000Z","msg":"聽日幾點"},{"pid":"3d8ec7c488eb2166282c38ff2d767d031323010b","tid":1369643,"uid":264724,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:01:49.000Z","msg":"求高人幫我整個靚啲嘅map"},{"pid":"360b37cb8c57a073b72f942ca160daf09152a